					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">That NMI handler really should start with PHA and then do PLA before returning. Otherwise it'll change the A register behind the main program's back.<br /><br />You write the destination address in OAM to $2003 and the source address in CPU memory to $4014, and then the APU stops the CPU to copy 256 bytes from the source into the PPU.</div>

